{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6d17ed6fe6","title":"我建议取消政治课","origin":"《右派言行集(下集)》 (全校学生中部分右派言行)，中共云南大学委员会编，一九五七年九月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08f0f374ab","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2499a730cb","name":"云南大学"},{"id":"424437ca7a","name":"阿窝"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"64859a05aa","type":"title","text":"我建议取消政治课","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"417a479b27","type":"authors","text":"云南大学阿窝","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"526ffa84aa","type":"subtitle","text":"我建议取消政治课　　历史系二年级  阿窝","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"c0dff82019","type":"paragraph","text":"我建议，我们来讨论一下政治课的问题，这是很多人头疼的问题。为此，我把春雷第一期上的小调主要论点重述一下。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"9946b9249e","type":"paragraph","text":"一、政治课质量不高，老是背教条，没有什么新东西，又不能密切反映当前社会实际。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"6cb0bcc233","type":"paragraph","text":"二、教员水平低，但却喜欢摆架子，强调政治课特殊地位，有意无意的抬高自己身份。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"de358925d2","type":"paragraph","text":"三、政治课教研室脱离群众，他们住在校外，不接近同学，既不了解社会生活(并非完全不了解)，又不知道同学的思想实际。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"8b6be19594","type":"paragraph","text":"四、因此，我主张政治课全面改革，使之有血有肉，否则取消——我所谓“滚蛋”，就是取消的意思。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"bf76423891","type":"paragraph","text":"就历史系的情况完全可以取消政治课，把它并入专史课中，这样对大家都有好处，教师可以做其他教学或研究工作，以免造成冗员。这些意见希望能得到安欣、老实诸君鸿论的指示。(刊于“民主墙”)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"2562c2a76e","type":"subtitle","text":"政治课(仿山西民歌) 　历史系二年级  阿窝","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"1c9db07a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"提起政治课","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"5f8f806dc9","type":"paragraph","text":"人人摆老(脑)壳","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"f80380bf87","type":"paragraph","text":"翻来覆去背教条","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"2bb1404558","type":"paragraph","text":"谁有心肠学","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"608c739fc5","type":"paragraph","text":"人大研究生","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"441aa8b3b9","type":"paragraph","text":"两年转回程","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"9076dfff0b","type":"paragraph","text":"云南大学任教员","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"8fca333970","type":"paragraph","text":"宣读笔记本","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"bf72f0fb76","type":"paragraph","text":"先生念笔记","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"7eb336d115","type":"paragraph","text":"学生打字机","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"5a277cfa41","type":"paragraph","text":"下课考试背笔记","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"2022b85350","type":"paragraph","text":"这算啥东西","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"8ff5432145","type":"paragraph","text":"肚里货色少","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"04bce4e7ef","type":"paragraph","text":"样子怪吓人","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"b9c865b27c","type":"paragraph","text":"动不动叩(扣)大帽子","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6d17ed6fe6"},{"id":"a38ff8b561","type":"paragraph","text":"政治不关心","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articl